  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction Trading Supplies</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Paya Lebar, East Region</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday to Friday, 8.30AM – 6PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic up to $3,000 + Comm + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Proactively identify and pursue new sales opportunities</li><li>Manage and grow existing client relationships, delivering excellent customer service and exceeding sales targets</li><li>Provide expert product and service knowledge to customers, effectively addressing their needs and queries</li><li>Work closely with our sales team to support pre-sales activities including client and site visits, tenders, submitting proposals, etc.</li><li>Accurately forecast sales, monitor pipeline and report on progress to management</li><li>Stay up to date with market trends, competitor activity and industry developments</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 years' experience in a sales role, preferably in building construction</li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Excellent negotiation and problem-solving skills</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80871 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
